{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Increase funding to \u00a320m yearly for male suicide prevention & support.",
        "additional_details": "Suicide is the biggest cause of death for men under 50 year olds in the UK. We believe this is a crisis that is ignored & brushed under the carpet. Funding, Prevention, Support & Awareness needs to be increased to at least \u00a320m per year for the UK. In England and Wales, suicide is three times more common in men than in women.",
        "background": "Increase funding to \u00a320m per year for the UK. Increase support, prevention & awareness. As its not spoke about enough.",
